text: Wolfratshausen (German pronunciation: [vɔlfʁaːtsˈhaʊzn̩]; West Central Bavarian: Woifradshausn) is a town in Bad Tölz-Wolfratshausen, a district (Landkreis) in Upper Bavaria. == References == ==Other websites== * Wolfratshausen website * Map * Article in the Economist (Aug 08) Category:Bad Tölz-Wolfratshausen
